Cliffjumper groaned at the words of Iron Raptor. He jumped of his feet,
and transformed in mid air, landing with a thud on the ground in his
small car mode. Firedrill turned his attention, "What?" He started, but
Cliffjumper reved his engine, and then in two seconds roared out towards
the open land at 300mph, tearing up the ground. "Don't worry kid, i'll
be back" he shouted. Beachcomber turned around and transformed as well.
"He's probably just going to blow of some steam, I hope" he said. "I'd
better go keep and eye on him" he finished in a cool tone, burning out
at his highest speed, significantly lower than Cliffjumper's.

Firedrill looked on, a bit worried. He turned to Sublime. "Ummmmmm, i'm
not sure what theyre going to do." he said.
